msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, you've become a regular like the rest of us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Seriously. You fit in so well, it's hard to imagine you not being here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "You're one to talk. You were so cold to him at first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Th-That's not true. Right, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Heh, I dunno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Being kind is the best way to deal with strangers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Otherwise you might treat someone in a way you regret."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Hearing that from you kinda pisses me off..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Being afraid of strangers is pretty much part of my personality now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "They say it's hard to change your personality once you're over 20."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "So age 20 is like a turning point..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "I need to be more accepting of new people."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Oh my, what a positive mindset, Kaneko-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Did hell just freeze over?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Guess I shouldn't be nice to you, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Wha- Why...!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Isn't life better when everyone has a different personality?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Everyone has their quirks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Yeah, good or bad, it's better to have a bunch of unique people."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "You might be right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Huh? What did you say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "S-Sorry, I was thinking about something else..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Sheesh, pay attention."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "The personality thing is true, but I also gave up on dreams after 20."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Maybe you woke up to reality?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "I still dream of becoming a singing and dancing carpenter!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Someday, you'll see me singing on TV for New Year's Eve!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "I forgot Gen-san was a carpenter. First I've heard of New Year's, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "People's personalities really show in their ambitions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Gen-san's sounds kinda irresponsible..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Do you have any ambitions, Mama?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Ambitions, hm."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Maybe build up a second and third bar to conquer Onomichi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "You could open up in Tokyo's business district! Kamurocho, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Tokyo, huh? I've never thought about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Hm, I dunno if I like the idea of Mama becoming super successful."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "I get it. I don't really like the thought either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Whaaat? Why not?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "You know, it's kinda like when a band you love starts selling out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Am I the same as a band?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "You're similar in the way that we're all your fans."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Oh my, that was sweet of you to say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "That's what I was gonna saaay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Liar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Huh? What did you say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Oh, sorry. I couldn't organize my thoughts..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Geez, pay attention..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Don't expand the business, Mama. Don't go to Tokyo either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Yeah, you'd be too far away from us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "What? You guys are being silly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "A simple life by the water is perfect for me, so don't worry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "But wouldn't to you guys just find another bar if I left?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "We're gonna stay devoted to your bar, Mama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Really? Then it makes sense to stay here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "You guys better keep stopping by to support me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "We know that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Leave it to us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "This place calms me down. You guys are like my family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "You HAVE a family, Hatakeyama-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "So I have two families."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Can you say that in front of your daughter?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Er... well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Haha, but you're more or less right. This place feels like home."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "My worries go away when I drink with the rest of the regulars."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "\"Regulars\" are a surprisingly important thing for a bar to have."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Y'know, I've never even thought about that until now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Maybe it's because a new wind blew through."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "A new wind?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "That's obviously Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Absolutely. Kiryu-san listened to all of our troubles."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "You're a broad-minded man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Sounds like you've really helped everyone here, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "I'm lookin' forward to more great times with you, rookie!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "He doesn't really come off as a rookie."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "You guys..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "To a future filled with delicious drinks!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "So let's toast!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Wait, I lost my train of thought..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Come on, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "You have to end with a baaaang."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "S-Sorry..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "(If only I had something to say...)"
msgstr ""

